"1.2](http://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap/v1.2/CAP-v1.2-os.html). "
"Construído com base no incrível [Wagtail CMS](https://wagtail.org)"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:17
msgid ""
"Preview a CAP alert as you edit. Save drafts for sharing with colleagues and"
