msgid "**Dynamic Matrix**"
msgstr "**Matriz Dinâmica**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Dynamic Matrix type is similar to a [Multiple-Choice "
"Matrix](https://surveyjs.io/survey-creator/documentation/end-user-"
"guide#multiple-choice-matrix), but respondents can add and remove matrix "
"rows."
msgstr ""
"O tipo de matriz dinâmica é semelhante a uma [matriz de múltipla "
"escolha](https://surveyjs.io/survey-creator/documentation/end-user-"
