"**Feature Block Items** - this section allows addition of a series of "
"alternating blocks containing an image, title, description and call to "
"action button."
msgstr ""
"**Itens do bloco de recursos** - esta seção permite a adição de uma série de"
" blocos alternados contendo uma imagem, título, descrição e botão de call to"
" action."

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Services.md:91
msgid ""
"![Feature Block "
"Sections](../../_static/images/services/feature_block_section.png \"Projects"
" Sections\")"
msgstr ""
"![Seções do bloco de "
"recursos](../../_static/images/services/feature_block_section.png \"Seções "
"de projetos\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Services.md:91
#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/manage_organisation/Manage-About.md:57
#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/manage_organisation/Manage-Projects.md:53
