#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:22
msgid ""
"Next, you need to create an environment file that contains the necessary "
"configuration for the development environment. You can do this by copying "
"the sample dev environment file provided in the repository:"
msgstr ""
"Em seguida, você precisa criar um arquivo de ambiente que contenha a "
